two ways to run serengeti in tomcat:

1. in Maven cli: execute "mvn tomcat:run -s maven-settings.xml" after running "mvn clean -s maven-settings.xml" and "mvn package -s maven-settings.xml"

2. in Eclipse (configure your Tomcat server properly first)
   a). edit Properties->Project Facets and add the Dynamic Web Module 2.5 to the serengeti project.
   b). edit Properties->Deployment Assembly and add the target/serengeti/WEB-INF/lib to the Deploy path /WEB-INF/lib
   c). run the serengeti project on server
